        <body>
            <div1 type="postcard">
        	    <pb entity="DSSR_000001108_0001"/>
        	    <opener>
        	        <address><name>M<hi rend="super">c</hi>Connell<lb/>
        	        Section Sanitaire<lb/>
        	            Americain Y<lb/>
        	            Paris
        	        </name>
        	        </address>
        	        <lb/>
        	        <lb/>
        	        <address><name>Paul Rockwell<lb/>
        	            Ward 170 l’hopital d’Ambulance<lb/>
        	            Americain<lb/>
        	            Neuilly-sur-Seine</name></address>
        	    </opener>
                
                <figure rend="page"><head>R&#x00E9; Fran&#x00E7;aise<lb/>Carte Postale</head></figure>
        		
           <div2 type="note">     
               <pb entity="DSSR_000001108_0002"/>
               <head>J. R. McC to Paul Rockwell <date value="1915-04-21">April 21<hi rend="super">st</hi>. [1915]</date></head>
           <opener>
           <dateline><date value="1915-04-21">April 21<hi rend="super">st</hi>. [1915]</date></dateline>
           	</opener>
           
           <p>
           I’ve sent you several<lb/>
           postals but neglected to<lb/>
               get them stamped after<lb/>
               putting F.M. on them.<lb/>
               Therefore this one to<lb/>
               make sure you have my <lb/>
               address:<lb/><lb/>
           
           Section Sanitaire Americaine<lb/>
               Y<lb/>
               Convoi d’Automobiles<lb/>
               Paris</p>
           <p>       
               Sent you a card from<lb/>
               Nancy to day.  We’ve<lb/>
               been postponed until<lb/>
               to morrow morning on our<lb/>
               trip to our post.  A<lb/>
               French sergeant has been<lb/>
               attached to the outfit.<lb/>
           </p>
        		
        	<closer>	
        	    <signed>J.R. M<hi rend="super">c.</hi>C</signed>
        		</closer>
           
         
           </div2>
            </div1>
        </body>
